# Authentication-policy material — fleet-internal, never published.
# These files contain SSH pubkey lists that reveal fleet topology
# (which workstations have access to which Jetson / Pi devices). The
# .example sibling alongside each is the committed documentation.
#
# Operator workflow: copy your fleet's real authorized_keys into the
# matching path before running bitbake. If missing, the recipe build
# fails fast with a pointer to this file.
recipes-core/nclawzero-ssh-keys/files/authorized_keys
recipes-core/nclawzero-rescue/files/authorized_keys
